Windows Registry Editor Version 5.00
; Disables Virtualization-Based Security (VBS) to improve system performance.
; This key disables virtualization-based security that protects critical system processes by isolating them.
; Disabling it may improve performance but lowers protection against advanced attacks.

[HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\DeviceGuard]
"EnableVirtualizationBasedSecurity"=dword:00000000